{"tid":2275859,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"學生企硬舉辦展覽  校方：違法即介入","createTime":"2020-11-07T13:01:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T14:07:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b32a2a9deb4b7557b054c7f73ebadfcb760b33d7","tid":2275859,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T13:01:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201107/GHV2O2L4SJHPRCLFDLXEUBQY4A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201107%2FGHV2O2L4SJHPRCLFDLXEUBQY4A%2F&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuNgc6rz%2Ba6PLwHdujBQ9FQE%3D&h=028c7971\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201107%2FGHV2O2L4SJHPRCLFDLXEUBQY4A%2F&h=c1f5edf5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201107/GHV2O2L4SJHPRCLFDLXEUBQY4A/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n學生企硬舉辦展覽  校方：違法即介入<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uzBi2f9mvhD6JRzxut173l-bzjg=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/76WYPUJSLBAQLJOXSPU2IDGFTM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuzBi2f9mvhD6JRzxut173l-bzjg%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F76WYPUJSLBAQLJOXSPU2IDGFTM.jpg&h=cc08c1f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中大學生會決定下周按計劃在文化廣場舉辦保衞戰一周年紀念展覽。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中大學生會擬下周在校園舉辦「中大保衞戰」紀念活動，.......................................。學生表示紀念活動將按計劃進行。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：指控性暴遭質疑 吳傲雪：可對簿公堂<br />\n<br />\n中大學生會幹事會周三獲校方告知「中大保衞戰」一周年回顧活動宣傳海報內含「光復香港，時代革命」旗幟，涉嫌違法，而且不當使用校長段崇智及前校長沈祖堯頭像，要求刪除海報。<br />\n<br />\n中大學生報引述學生代表稱，大學輔導長周四與幹事會臨時行政委員會、各書院學生會及代表會時委會成員會面，就如何舉辦「中大保衞戰」一周年活動討論。輔導長指，校方認為該海報涉違法所以必須介入，但表明不是不允許舉辦有關活動。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：公開信指聲援學生致中大衝突  四警協會批鬥段崇智促認錯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或自行移除展品<br />\n<br />\n據報道，輔導長向學生指現階段限聚令仍實施，.................................<br />\n<br />\n學生代表要求輔導長澄清法律紅線問題，輔導長沒正面回答，僅指要視乎表達方式及個案，如果那「八個字」是屬於新聞報道，相信不受影響，但如果屬於煽惑他人進行違法行為，就是違法。大學會先徵詢法律意見，如有違法風險會提醒及介入。<br />\n<br />\n對於宣傳品及展品會否被校方移除，報道引述輔導長警告，校方會透過緊急對話機制先與負責人對話，但不能保證對話時間，如沒共識就會自行移除認為違法的物品。"},{"pid":"a8a35bf48adee202328d590e6edd2c943fb38ca2","tid":2275859,"uid":289694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T13:06:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b04cf777ffdc154e47ffeaafa7a45ea55c52e59","tid":2275859,"uid":139199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T13:33:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c037dea48943b0dbcdd2a1bc13c85a3d7d0a1d5","tid":2275859,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T14:02:54.000Z","msg":"幾號搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965dbad253af44839c7504f5537e07e8bdd38e36","tid":2275859,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T14:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4749101f2826424feefc4402228c2ef4a506ddf2","tid":2275859,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T14:07:07.000Z","msg":"推"}]}